{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2018-10-11/One-yuan-coin","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"e16aa46c-73a7-5e46-87e8-e86bec991346","html":"<h3>润物细无声 —— 影响无处不在</h3>\n<p>一元钱硬币，能做什么？<br>\n经济学家眼里：一元钱硬币是货币流通的代表。<br>\n哲学家眼里：一元钱硬币是事物的多面性。<br>\n科学家眼里：一元钱硬币是物质的构成、属性等。<br>\n小商贩眼里：一元钱硬币是利润。<br>\n收藏家眼里：一元钱硬币是收藏价值。<br>\n……    </p>\n<p>在刚学会说话的小朋友眼里，一元钱硬币是什么呢？      </p>\n<p>【故事回忆】时光回到辰宝一岁多，刚学会说话的时候<br>\n【趣事小情景】<br>\n辰宝一岁多，刚学会说话，偶尔蹦出几句“新词”能让身边的大人们笑得前俯后仰。有一次跟外婆回老家，从城市到农村，由约束到自由，辰宝发挥着所有小宝宝都拥有的好奇，打量着农村的新奇事务。<br>\n晕车的外婆，长途行车颠簸之后的疲惫还未消失，就在整理床铺。<br>\n一旁帮忙收拾东西的我，看着辰宝的外婆忙碌，时不时关注下辰宝，确认他在安全活动范围。<br>\n外婆：我准备整理床铺，你帮我看着一下辰宝。    </p>\n<p><em>我在一旁拿着被单，准备帮忙铺床</em>.<br>\n<em>一声清脆的响声，嘀铃铃……</em>   </p>\n<p>外婆：什么东西掉出来了？<br>\n我：好像是一个硬币。   </p>\n<p><em>待我还没反应过来，硬币掉到哪里的时候，辰宝已经爬到床底下，捡到那个硬币.</em><br>\n<em>外婆怕辰宝将硬币误食~</em>    </p>\n<p>外婆：辰宝，硬币拿过来，外婆帮你保管……   </p>\n<p><em>我准备去从辰宝手中拿过硬币，他机灵的小身躯已经从床底下溜出，小步慢跑到房间门口</em>   </p>\n<p>辰宝：不，我自己管着……买车买房……<br>\n我：哈哈o(∩_∩)o 哈哈~ 谁，谁，跟谁学的“买车买房”……   </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 540px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/09d21/mooncakes.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mooncakes\"\n        title=\"mooncakes\"\n        src=\"/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/09d21/mooncakes.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/e07e9/mooncakes.jpg 200w,\n/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/066f9/mooncakes.jpg 400w,\n/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/09d21/mooncakes.jpg 540w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","fields":{"slug":"2018-10-11/One-yuan-coin","prefix":"2018-10-11"},"frontmatter":{"title":"One yuan coin","author":"文:Jane, 图(月饼):贝贝","category":["funny"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/71875f6ebcea59a7566fc9255b7d8f32/9dc27/mooncakes.jpg"}}}}},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"2018-10-12/remember-me","prefix":"2018-10-12"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Remember me"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"2018-10-10/I-am-a-human-being","prefix":"2018-10-10"},"frontmatter":{"title":"I am a human being."}},"authornote":{"id":"86780e07-dd43-5b96-827f-d5867264385a","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"2018-10-11/One-yuan-coin","total":57,"prev":"2018-10-12/remember-me","next":"2018-10-10/I-am-a-human-being"}}}